261
00:11:25,360 --> 00:11:25,960
That's right.

262
00:11:25,960 --> 00:11:27,290
Fang, you go back first.

263
00:11:27,720 --> 00:11:29,520
Go with Lu to see what's going on.

264
00:11:30,120 --> 00:11:30,450
Okay.

265
00:11:31,150 --> 00:11:33,440
Royal eggs! Royal walnuts!

266
00:11:34,440 --> 00:11:35,000
Come on!

267
00:11:35,750 --> 00:11:37,960
