557
00:20:58,680 --> 00:20:59,540
I'll wait then.

558
00:20:59,960 --> 00:21:01,890
I'll walk around with Heizui first

559
00:21:02,110 --> 00:21:03,070
to see what's going on.

560
00:21:03,070 --> 00:21:04,530
Come on, come on, this way.

561
00:21:05,220 --> 00:21:05,750
Let's go.

562
00:21:16,350 --> 00:21:17,750
Who's that? Who? Who?

563
00:21:18,240 --> 00:21:18,680
Who?

564
00:21:18,680 --> 00:21:20,200
The password, quick, say the password!

565
00:21:20,200 --> 00:21:21,460
Beef and mutton paomo.

566
00:21:21,750 --> 00:21:23,150
Spicy garlic lamb blood.

567
00:21:23,590 --> 00:21:24,240
Kun.

568
00:21:25,070 --> 00:21:25,920
You scared us.

569
00:21:26,510 --> 00:21:27,370
Any situation?

570
00:21:28,790 --> 00:21:29,990
We patrolled around,

571
00:21:30,400 --> 00:21:32,000
but didn't find anything unusual.

572
00:21:32,000 --> 00:21:33,400
I have some information.

573
00:21:33,680 --> 00:21:35,750
The Cultural Relics Management Office
said they'd come patrol together,

574
00:21:35,750 --> 00:21:36,480
but not a single one showed up.

575
00:21:36,480 --> 00:21:37,610
Not one of them came?

576
00:21:38,070 --> 00:21:39,550
They're fattening the fat

577
00:21:39,550 --> 00:21:41,110
and squeezing the lean.

578
00:21:41,310 --> 00:21:43,310
The Du Mausoleum and Phoenix Mountain
are like their own children,

579
00:21:43,310 --> 00:21:45,720
while this big tomb in Yin Village
isn't their own kid.

580
00:21:45,720 --> 00:21:47,380
Alright, uncle, don't worry.

581
00:21:47,830 --> 00:21:48,680
It's like this,

582
00:21:48,680 --> 00:21:50,480
I'll go to the Cultural Relics Management
Office to talk to their director

583
00:21:50,480 --> 00:21:51,400
and see what's going on.

584
00:21:51,400 --> 00:21:51,730
Okay.

585
00:21:51,790 --> 00:21:52,190
Mr. Lu,

586
00:21:52,350 --> 00:21:53,440
thank you for your hard work tonight.

587
00:21:53,440 --> 00:21:54,720
Keep Uncle Shoucun company.

588
00:21:54,720 --> 00:21:55,250
Alright.

589
00:21:55,310 --> 00:21:55,920
Be careful.

590
00:21:55,920 --> 00:21:56,590
Okay, okay.

591
00:21:56,750 --> 00:21:57,280
Alright.

592
00:21:57,400 --> 00:21:58,460
You be careful too.

593
00:21:58,480 --> 00:21:59,310
Heizui.

594
00:21:59,480 --> 00:22:00,240
Let's go, let's go.

595
00:22:00,240 --> 00:22:00,770
Let's go.

596
00:22:11,230 --> 00:22:13,630
Shoucun called you to find someone, right?

597
00:22:14,050 --> 00:22:14,600
Mr. Fang.

598
00:22:16,960 --> 00:22:17,830
As you can see,

599
00:22:18,070 --> 00:22:19,550
I'm the only one left here.

600
00:22:20,510 --> 00:22:23,590
I'm about to go support
the Du Mausoleum in a bit.

601
00:22:24,030 --> 00:22:24,920
Our people

602
00:22:25,400 --> 00:22:27,640
are like head-bobbing chickens,

603
00:22:27,830 --> 00:22:30,400
always darting around, never idle.

604
00:22:30,920 --> 00:22:31,720
What can we do?

605
00:22:31,960 --> 00:22:33,160
Look, since I came in,

606
00:22:33,310 --> 00:22:33,910
until now,

607
00:22:34,510 --> 00:22:36,910
have I said anything about needing people?

608
00:22:37,060 --> 00:22:38,920
I know it's difficult for you too.

609
00:22:40,270 --> 00:22:43,310
Today, we originally arranged
for Chen to go to Yin Village.

610
00:22:43,310 --> 00:22:45,440
But Phoenix Mountain was short-staffed.

611
00:22:45,440 --> 00:22:46,920
They all went to help there.

612
00:22:46,920 --> 00:22:48,170
Only Section Chief Wu

613
00:22:48,660 --> 00:22:51,720
and another comrade are left
to guard the Du Mausoleum.

614
00:22:52,750 --> 00:22:53,680
Here's the case.

615
00:22:54,030 --> 00:22:55,160
In the next few days,

616
00:22:55,510 --> 00:22:57,200
I'll keep holding on with

617
00:22:57,200 --> 00:22:58,660
our archaeological team.

618
00:22:58,790 --> 00:22:59,520
Is that okay?

619
00:22:59,640 --> 00:23:00,200
But for this matter,

620
00:23:00,200 --> 00:23:02,330
you need to think of a way to help me out.

621
00:23:04,110 --> 00:23:04,640
Mr. Fang,

622
00:23:05,550 --> 00:23:07,080
I actually have a solution.

623
00:23:07,640 --> 00:23:09,370
But only you can make it happen.

624
00:23:10,480 --> 00:23:10,830
Go on.

625
00:23:11,830 --> 00:23:13,440
The grand tomb in Yin Village,

626
00:23:13,440 --> 00:23:15,070
it's unidentified and unclaimed.

627
00:23:15,070 --> 00:23:17,470
Naturally, we can't allocate people to it.

628
00:23:18,030 --> 00:23:19,640
However, if you can prove

629
00:23:19,640 --> 00:23:21,640
its historical and cultural value,

630
00:23:22,000 --> 00:23:24,200
clarify the identity of the tomb owner,

631
00:23:25,270 --> 00:23:27,600
and turn it into a cultural heritage site,

632
00:23:28,480 --> 00:23:32,210
then cultural protection resources
will naturally be allocated.

633
00:23:33,350 --> 00:23:34,410
Do you understand?

634
00:23:35,830 --> 00:23:36,640
Director Zhang,

635
00:23:36,640 --> 00:23:37,790
here's the case.

636
00:23:38,400 --> 00:23:39,240
In our Yin Village,

637
00:23:39,240 --> 00:23:40,960
the current situation
of cultural heritage protection

638
00:23:40,960 --> 00:23:41,890
is quite severe.

639
00:23:42,310 --> 00:23:43,790
Can we think of a way

640
00:23:44,480 --> 00:23:46,610
to increase the funding or something,

641
00:23:46,750 --> 00:23:49,070
like adding some security positions?

642
00:23:49,210 --> 00:23:50,210
What do you think?

643
00:23:52,310 --> 00:23:54,170
There's no need for that anymore.

644
00:23:54,510 --> 00:23:54,880
Why?

645
00:23:58,720 --> 00:24:00,440
Our excavation plan has been rejected.

646
00:24:00,440 --> 00:24:00,770
What?

647
00:24:01,440 --> 00:24:02,160
Why is that?

648
00:24:02,750 --> 00:24:04,160
Why? Why?

649
00:24:04,640 --> 00:24:06,070
Why so many "whys"?

650
00:24:06,960 --> 00:24:08,550
Because the higher-ups think

651
00:24:08,550 --> 00:24:11,400
we don't have experience
in excavating large tombs.

652
00:24:11,400 --> 00:24:12,790
Because the recent public opinion

653
00:24:12,790 --> 00:24:13,850
is not in our favor.

654
00:24:16,590 --> 00:24:17,590
Because we are now

655
00:24:18,830 --> 00:24:22,030
already facing skepticism
from the academic community.

656
00:24:27,680 --> 00:24:30,740
They won't let us
excavate because we lack experience.

657
00:24:30,880 --> 00:24:33,350
If we don't excavate,
we'll never gain experience.

658
00:24:33,350 --> 00:24:35,680
Isn't this just an endless vicious cycle?

659
00:24:41,640 --> 00:24:42,840
A life given at birth,

660
00:24:43,790 --> 00:24:45,120
a scale nailed in place.

661
00:24:45,960 --> 00:24:46,400
We

662
00:24:47,920 --> 00:24:49,580
just have to accept this fate.

663
00:24:57,400 --> 00:24:57,790
Fang.

664
00:25:00,250 --> 00:25:01,180
Let's pull back.

665
00:25:14,270 --> 00:25:14,800
Mr. Zhao.

666
00:25:16,870 --> 00:25:17,310
Mr. Mu.

667
00:25:17,920 --> 00:25:18,590
Youre' here.

668
00:25:18,590 --> 00:25:18,880
I'm here.

669
00:25:18,880 --> 00:25:19,700
Please, have a seat.

670
00:25:19,700 --> 00:25:20,230
Alright.

671
00:25:21,310 --> 00:25:22,000
I

672
00:25:22,590 --> 00:25:24,240
am very seriously

673
00:25:24,400 --> 00:25:26,160
studying your monograph.

674
00:25:26,350 --> 00:25:27,770
You've become
quite impressive now, haven't you?

675
00:25:27,770 --> 00:25:29,430
You've even become an author.

676
00:25:29,920 --> 00:25:31,240
What author?

677
00:25:31,790 --> 00:25:33,070
I just scribbled it down.

678
00:25:33,070 --> 00:25:34,240
You've written this well.

679
00:25:34,240 --> 00:25:36,100
Look at what you've
written here.

680
00:25:36,510 --> 00:25:37,720
The expressive and
exaggerated artistic style

681
00:25:37,720 --> 00:25:40,270
of Han dynasty pottery figurines
was closely linked

682
00:25:40,270 --> 00:25:42,030
to a combination of factors,
including the political culture

683
00:25:42,030 --> 00:25:45,510
and aesthetic consciousness of the time.

684
00:25:46,590 --> 00:25:49,440
It embodies
unique national characteristics

685
00:25:49,440 --> 00:25:50,880
and cultural connotations,

686
00:25:50,880 --> 00:25:54,070
reflecting ancient Chinese
philosophical thoughts.

687
00:25:55,270 --> 00:25:56,470
To be honest with you,

688
00:25:56,490 --> 00:25:58,090
I recognize all these words,

689
00:25:58,640 --> 00:26:00,550
but I don't understand
any of their meanings.

690
00:26:00,550 --> 00:26:01,750
I just don't understand

691
00:26:01,750 --> 00:26:03,010
why you intellectuals

692
00:26:03,550 --> 00:26:05,110
can't just call a hen a hen.

693
00:26:05,110 --> 00:26:07,440
Why insist on calling it a rooster's wife?

694
00:26:08,670 --> 00:26:11,120
I just said I scribbled it down.

695
00:26:11,920 --> 00:26:12,550
You see,

696
00:26:13,270 --> 00:26:16,330
if it weren't for those friends
at the publishing house

697
00:26:16,550 --> 00:26:17,310
exaggerating and praising,

698
00:26:17,310 --> 00:26:19,440
I wouldn't dare to show such timidity.

699
00:26:19,720 --> 00:26:20,790
Let's talk about the main issue.

700
00:26:20,790 --> 00:26:21,320
Mr. Zhao,

701
00:26:21,720 --> 00:26:23,750
I'm here today to congratulate you.

702
00:26:24,920 --> 00:26:25,780
Congratulate?

703
00:26:25,990 --> 00:26:27,720
What's there to congratulate?

704
00:26:28,070 --> 00:26:29,110
You're now

705
00:26:29,110 --> 00:26:31,960
the president
of our Qinchuan Antique Association.

706
00:26:31,960 --> 00:26:33,990
Of course, I should congratulate you.

707
00:26:33,990 --> 00:26:36,240
What's that all about?

708
00:26:36,240 --> 00:26:37,440
I can't compare to you in this.

709
00:26:37,440 --> 00:26:39,310
I, I just can't compare.

710
00:26:39,310 --> 00:26:41,240
I don't understand any of this.

711
00:26:42,880 --> 00:26:43,830
But let me tell you,

712
00:26:43,830 --> 00:26:44,830
this book of yours

713
00:26:45,310 --> 00:26:46,170
is really good.

714
00:26:46,310 --> 00:26:48,510
I plan to get some more

715
00:26:49,030 --> 00:26:50,400
and bring them to the association

716
00:26:50,400 --> 00:26:52,240
to let those folks study it well.

717
00:26:53,000 --> 00:26:55,460
If you're going to
publish another edition,

718
00:26:55,830 --> 00:26:56,640
I'll ask Qin

719
00:26:57,380 --> 00:26:58,640
to write a postscript for you.

720
00:26:58,640 --> 00:26:59,500
I'm flattered.

721
00:26:59,750 --> 00:27:00,880
This is a lousy book.

722
00:27:01,000 --> 00:27:02,730
How could I trouble Qin with it?

723
00:27:03,200 --> 00:27:06,030
A nobody like me

724
00:27:06,510 --> 00:27:09,480
should just mind my own business.

725
00:27:11,310 --> 00:27:13,310
You're just being too modest.

726
00:27:14,160 --> 00:27:15,090
But that's good.

727
00:27:15,640 --> 00:27:16,200
Modesty

728
00:27:16,960 --> 00:27:18,020
leads to progress,

729
00:27:18,270 --> 00:27:18,810
right?

730
00:27:20,030 --> 00:27:21,560
We're all ordinary people.

731
00:27:22,440 --> 00:27:24,300
What's the use of being arrogant?

732
00:27:24,350 --> 00:27:26,000
Nothing good comes from human arrogance.

733
00:27:26,000 --> 00:27:27,750
A dog's arrogance is just a pile of shit.

734
00:27:27,750 --> 00:27:29,080
For us ordinary people,

735
00:27:29,200 --> 00:27:32,240
the most important thing
is to earn money honestly

736
00:27:32,610 --> 00:27:33,830
and put it in our own pockets.

737
00:27:33,830 --> 00:27:34,830
That's the truth.

738
00:27:35,790 --> 00:27:37,120
Mr. Zhao, you're right.

739
00:27:37,790 --> 00:27:39,590
Nothing's more real than money.

740
00:27:42,550 --> 00:27:43,270
Recently,

741
00:27:44,180 --> 00:27:46,910
that big tomb in Yin Village
has been quite a hype.

742
00:27:48,370 --> 00:27:51,100
Who knows how many
troublemakers it'll attract.

743
00:27:52,160 --> 00:27:53,000
What I mean is,

744
00:27:53,590 --> 00:27:55,650
you shouldn't join in the commotion.

745
00:27:56,550 --> 00:27:59,730
Your people have been
causing quite a stir there lately,

746
00:27:59,790 --> 00:28:01,190
with all that bloodshed.

747
00:28:01,450 --> 00:28:02,710
It's too conspicuous.

748
00:28:04,590 --> 00:28:06,350
You're showing your hand too much.

749
00:28:06,350 --> 00:28:07,480
A small-time player

750
00:28:08,400 --> 00:28:09,920
should keep a low profile.

751
00:28:10,560 --> 00:28:11,820
That's real strength.

752
00:28:12,480 --> 00:28:13,020
Right?

753
00:28:15,480 --> 00:28:15,900
Right.

754
00:28:17,350 --> 00:28:18,150
I understand.

755
00:28:18,830 --> 00:28:19,360
Mr. Zhao,

756
00:28:19,640 --> 00:28:20,900
I'll take my leave now.

757
00:28:21,310 --> 00:28:21,840
Alright.

758
00:28:22,110 --> 00:28:23,350
I won't keep you for dinner.

759
00:28:23,350 --> 00:28:23,720
Okay.

760
00:28:23,880 --> 00:28:24,110
Okay.

761
00:28:24,110 --> 00:28:24,590
See you later.

762
00:28:24,590 --> 00:28:25,650
Alright, alright.

763
00:28:34,880 --> 00:28:37,120
Get lost.

764
00:28:41,400 --> 00:28:42,640
Let's pack up quickly.

765
00:28:42,640 --> 00:28:44,350
A bunch of people have already left.

766
00:28:44,350 --> 00:28:46,030
We've done everything we needed to do.

767
00:28:46,030 --> 00:28:47,090
The rest

768
00:28:47,120 --> 00:28:48,350
can't be solved by us.

769
00:28:50,830 --> 00:28:51,360
Mr. Fang,

770
00:28:52,270 --> 00:28:53,830
each to their own task.

771
00:28:54,440 --> 00:28:55,570
As archaeologists,

772
00:28:55,590 --> 00:28:58,320
we can't handle
cultural preservation matters.

773
00:29:01,310 --> 00:29:01,590
Kun.

774
00:29:02,720 --> 00:29:03,240
Master.

775
00:29:04,580 --> 00:29:05,990
Are you really leaving?

776
00:29:07,590 --> 00:29:08,120
Xiaoman,

777
00:29:08,720 --> 00:29:10,750
the excavation plan has been rejected.

778
00:29:10,750 --> 00:29:12,750
There's no point in us staying here.

779
00:29:12,920 --> 00:29:15,780
But your technical skills
are already proficient.

780
00:29:16,000 --> 00:29:18,000
Although the work
in Yin Village has stopped,

781
00:29:18,000 --> 00:29:20,510
if you still
want to continue in this field,

782
00:29:20,920 --> 00:29:22,350
you can contact me anytime.

783
00:29:22,350 --> 00:29:24,480
I'll help you find work at other sites.

784
00:29:24,950 --> 00:29:25,470
Okay?

785
00:29:29,680 --> 00:29:29,960
Kun.

786
00:29:33,200 --> 00:29:35,730
Don't worry
about the big tomb in Yin Village.

787
00:29:36,110 --> 00:29:37,880
The work at home isn't that busy.

788
00:29:37,880 --> 00:29:40,880
I'll come to relieve
Uncle Shoucun whenever I'm free.

789
00:29:40,880 --> 00:29:41,740
I don't believe

790
00:29:42,310 --> 00:29:43,310
that with us here,

791
00:29:43,480 --> 00:29:45,340
those thieves would dare to come.

792
00:29:45,400 --> 00:29:45,930
Xiaoman,

793
00:29:46,550 --> 00:29:48,150
you mustn't act recklessly.

794
00:29:48,200 --> 00:29:49,720
Those thieves are armed.

795
00:29:50,440 --> 00:29:52,240
Even grown men don't dare to get close.

796
00:29:52,240 --> 00:29:53,590
Let alone a young girl like you.

797
00:29:53,590 --> 00:29:55,190
Then what about Yin Village?

798
00:30:06,110 --> 00:30:06,680
Heizui?

799
00:30:11,720 --> 00:30:12,650
Why are you here?

800
00:30:14,590 --> 00:30:16,250
Don't you want us to leave too?

801
00:30:17,400 --> 00:30:17,860
Heizui,

802
00:30:18,350 --> 00:30:18,950
come here.

803
00:30:19,270 --> 00:30:20,310
What are you doing?

804
00:30:20,310 --> 00:30:20,910
Come here.

805
00:30:22,510 --> 00:30:22,970
Heizui,

806
00:30:24,100 --> 00:30:24,980
you good-for-nothing.

807
00:30:24,980 --> 00:30:26,310
What are you doing here?

808
00:30:27,550 --> 00:30:28,440
How thick-skinned you are.

809
00:30:28,440 --> 00:30:29,200
They're about to leave,

810
00:30:29,200 --> 00:30:30,000
and you're still here.

811
00:30:30,000 --> 00:30:31,600
Why are you clinging to them?

812
00:30:31,720 --> 00:30:33,450
You know we're adopted, right?

813
00:30:33,550 --> 00:30:34,590
Born to a stepmother.

814
00:30:34,590 --> 00:30:36,830
Whether they care
about Yin Village or not, we don't care.

815
00:30:36,830 --> 00:30:37,260
Let's go.

816
00:30:37,260 --> 00:30:38,520
Let's patrol. Come on.

817
00:30:54,680 --> 00:30:55,940
I'm not going anymore.

818
00:30:57,550 --> 00:30:57,880
What?

819
00:31:02,720 --> 00:31:04,320
I said I'm not going anymore.

820
00:31:04,920 --> 00:31:06,920
Did you get your head stuck in a door?

821
00:31:07,350 --> 00:31:08,440
We're from the Archaeology Institute.

822
00:31:08,440 --> 00:31:09,510
We're not cultural relic conservators.

823
00:31:09,510 --> 00:31:10,270
You're giving up your job?

824
00:31:10,270 --> 00:31:10,880
I quit.

825
00:31:11,680 --> 00:31:12,110
Kun,

826
00:31:13,190 --> 00:31:14,050
don't be hasty.

827
00:31:15,000 --> 00:31:15,460
This...

828
00:31:16,160 --> 00:31:17,090
This is our fate.

829
00:31:17,110 --> 00:31:19,310
The great tomb of Yin Village is my life.

830
00:31:20,750 --> 00:31:22,950
If the great tomb of Yin Village is gone,

831
00:31:23,640 --> 00:31:26,300
what's the point
of doing archaeology anymore?

832
00:31:36,960 --> 00:31:38,070
Up, up.

833
00:31:39,510 --> 00:31:39,840
Good.

834
00:31:40,440 --> 00:31:40,960
Go, up.

835
00:31:42,480 --> 00:31:44,270
When you see a bad guy,
you gotta pounce, got it?

836
00:31:44,270 --> 00:31:44,640
Come.

837
00:31:45,000 --> 00:31:45,400
Up.

838
00:31:46,880 --> 00:31:47,680
That's right.

839
00:31:49,200 --> 00:31:49,900
Heizui, up.

840
00:31:51,720 --> 00:31:52,130
Good.

841
00:31:53,270 --> 00:31:53,510
Go.

842
00:31:53,920 --> 00:31:54,160
Up.

843
00:31:55,350 --> 00:31:56,030
Very good.

844
00:31:56,640 --> 00:31:58,030
That's how you deal with bad guys.

845
00:31:58,030 --> 00:31:58,640
Heizui.

846
00:31:59,180 --> 00:31:59,710
Sit down.

847
00:32:00,280 --> 00:32:02,740
Didn't your archaeological team all leave?

848
00:32:02,830 --> 00:32:03,590
I missed you.

849
00:32:04,130 --> 00:32:05,590
Just came to see you again.

850
00:32:08,560 --> 00:32:09,830
Worried you might
get slack watching alone.

851
00:32:09,830 --> 00:32:10,680
I came to help.

852
00:32:10,790 --> 00:32:12,270
What kind of help are you offering me?

853
00:32:12,270 --> 00:32:12,960
-Come on.
-What do you mean?

854
00:32:12,960 --> 00:32:13,420
Heizui.

855
00:32:13,920 --> 00:32:14,260
Come.

856
00:32:14,400 --> 00:32:16,400
The Yin Village tomb
isn't just this piece of land,

857
00:32:16,400 --> 00:32:16,800
right?

858
00:32:17,160 --> 00:32:18,680
You can see other places too?

859
00:32:18,680 --> 00:32:20,550
I don't care,
I just need to watch this area.

860
00:32:20,550 --> 00:32:22,030
Your name is Yan Shoucun.

861
00:32:22,200 --> 00:32:23,570
You're not called Yan Shoudi.

862
00:32:23,570 --> 00:32:25,700
How can you just guard this small area?

863
00:32:26,030 --> 00:32:27,310
Why are you changing my name?

864
00:32:27,310 --> 00:32:28,240
You little brat.

865
00:32:28,270 --> 00:32:29,600
Are you messing with me?

866
00:32:29,680 --> 00:32:30,640
Alright, alright.

867
00:32:30,640 --> 00:32:31,760
Anyway, I'm going to quit my job.

868
00:32:31,760 --> 00:32:33,740
No matter what,
I'll squeeze in the shack with you.

869
00:32:33,740 --> 00:32:35,510
I'll help you guard it together.

870
00:32:35,510 --> 00:32:35,880
What?

871
00:32:37,750 --> 00:32:38,480
You...

872
00:32:38,840 --> 00:32:40,120
You want to live here?

873
00:32:42,000 --> 00:32:42,400
Uncle.

874
00:32:53,440 --> 00:32:53,840
Uncle.

875
00:32:54,440 --> 00:32:55,680
Now, in the village,

876
00:32:56,030 --> 00:32:57,960
only Uncle Shoucun is guarding it.

877
00:32:58,210 --> 00:32:59,810
Anyway, I'm about to resign,

878
00:33:00,240 --> 00:33:01,410
so now the two of us

879
00:33:01,440 --> 00:33:03,440
are taking turns patrolling there.

880
00:33:03,550 --> 00:33:05,270
But the area of the Yin Village great tomb

881
00:33:05,270 --> 00:33:06,130
is really vast,

882
00:33:06,480 --> 00:33:07,880
and we're short-handed.

883
00:33:08,200 --> 00:33:09,880
Everyone listens to what you say.

884
00:33:09,880 --> 00:33:12,720
Could you see if it's possible to organize
some cultural relic protection volunteers?

885
00:33:12,720 --> 00:33:13,350
So we can all together

886
00:33:13,350 --> 00:33:15,410
protect this Yin Village great tomb.

887
00:33:15,830 --> 00:33:17,200
The matter of the great tomb or not

888
00:33:17,200 --> 00:33:18,930
is the government's business.

889
00:33:19,790 --> 00:33:21,450
What does it have to do with me?

890
00:33:21,610 --> 00:33:22,750
Those buried beneath Yin Village

891
00:33:22,750 --> 00:33:24,880
are also the ancestors
from Yin Village.

892
00:33:24,880 --> 00:33:25,680
Isn't that so?

893
00:33:26,030 --> 00:33:27,400
We can't just stand by and watch

894
00:33:27,400 --> 00:33:28,680
outsiders desecrate our ancestors' graves...

895
00:33:28,680 --> 00:33:30,880
I'm now a family member of a tomb raider.

896
00:33:33,680 --> 00:33:35,210
The whole village knows it.

897
00:33:36,070 --> 00:33:36,920
What face do I have left...

898
00:33:36,920 --> 00:33:37,880
Uncle, no one considers you

899
00:33:37,880 --> 00:33:39,680
a family member of a tomb raider.

900
00:33:41,510 --> 00:33:43,110
The tongue is a sharp knife,

901
00:33:44,640 --> 00:33:46,440
it kills without drawing blood.

902
00:33:46,750 --> 00:33:48,350
Isn't it Lai who did this?

903
00:33:49,590 --> 00:33:50,790
The villagers are all watching.

904
00:33:50,790 --> 00:33:52,590
Our ancestors are watching too.

905
00:33:55,050 --> 00:33:57,450
It's like I've got
a piss cloud over my head,

906
00:33:58,110 --> 00:33:59,910
and the whole world's downwind.

907
00:34:02,830 --> 00:34:05,360
I'll never smell good
again in this lifetime.

908
00:34:12,080 --> 00:34:12,780
Kun,

909
00:34:14,250 --> 00:34:15,530
this matter of yours,

910
00:34:16,139 --> 00:34:17,469
I can't help you with it.

911
00:35:23,000 --> 00:35:24,070
Cooking up some explosives.

912
00:35:24,070 --> 00:35:25,600
It's about to suffocate me.

913
00:35:25,710 --> 00:35:26,880
It won't kill you, bro.

914
00:35:26,880 --> 00:35:29,230
You're digging stuff
out of a ghost's mouth.

915
00:35:29,230 --> 00:35:30,600
Even ghosts couldn't kill you.

916
00:35:30,600 --> 00:35:31,480
Ghosts couldn't kill me.

917
00:35:31,480 --> 00:35:32,940
But the explosives might.

918
00:35:33,040 --> 00:35:34,190
Your brother's
cooking up these explosives.

919
00:35:34,190 --> 00:35:35,440
Not sure if the ratio is right.

920
00:35:35,440 --> 00:35:36,440
Let me take a look.

921
00:35:37,190 --> 00:35:38,600
Let me take a look.
The ratio is good.

922
00:35:38,600 --> 00:35:40,130
You're a man of great deeds.

923
00:35:40,590 --> 00:35:41,990
What great deed am I up to?

924
00:35:42,750 --> 00:35:44,680
Don't know if it'll explode or not.

925
00:35:44,760 --> 00:35:45,420
Let's do it.

926
00:36:05,880 --> 00:36:06,410
How is it?

927
00:36:06,670 --> 00:36:09,150
"The thread in a loving mother's hand..."

928
00:36:09,510 --> 00:36:12,630
"The thread in a loving mother's hand..."

929
00:36:13,360 --> 00:36:16,290
"Becomes clothes
on her traveling child's back..."

930
00:36:16,760 --> 00:36:20,360
"Becomes clothes
on her traveling child's back..."

931
00:36:21,030 --> 00:36:22,230
This line means,

932
00:36:22,230 --> 00:36:23,550
a mother

933
00:36:24,070 --> 00:36:27,480
is mending clothes
for her child who's about to travel far.

934
00:36:28,480 --> 00:36:31,030
"Before departure, she sews with care..."

935
00:36:31,360 --> 00:36:35,230
"Before departure, she sews with care..."

936
00:36:35,510 --> 00:36:38,190
"Fearing the child's late return."

937
00:36:46,700 --> 00:36:48,320
Is Yan Xiaowu your father?

938
00:36:53,840 --> 00:36:55,040
I don't have a father.

939
00:37:22,800 --> 00:37:23,230
Guang.

940
00:37:24,590 --> 00:37:24,880
Brother.

941
00:37:24,880 --> 00:37:25,970
Did you bring all the books?

942
00:37:25,970 --> 00:37:26,510
I brought them all.

943
00:37:26,510 --> 00:37:26,930
Good.

944
00:37:27,860 --> 00:37:29,230
[Children's Extracurricular Reading]

945
00:37:29,230 --> 00:37:30,320
Let's go, move them in.

946
00:37:30,320 --> 00:37:30,850
Brother,

947
00:37:31,150 --> 00:37:32,750
I have something to tell you.

948
00:37:33,360 --> 00:37:33,960
What is it?

949
00:37:34,320 --> 00:37:36,250
Do you know who's come to Qinchuan?

950
00:37:36,510 --> 00:37:36,840
Who?

951
00:37:37,480 --> 00:37:38,010
King Hua.

952
00:37:39,360 --> 00:37:41,100
I think he's after

953
00:37:41,230 --> 00:37:42,760
the big tomb in Yin Village.

954
00:37:42,800 --> 00:37:45,200
He's been hanging around there these days.

955
00:37:45,320 --> 00:37:47,450
We've taken all the goods in Qinchuan.

956
00:37:48,030 --> 00:37:50,960
He used to be a tiger,
now he's barely a scrawny stray.

957
00:37:51,800 --> 00:37:53,400
There's a big haul this time.

958
00:37:53,800 --> 00:37:56,580
It's understandable
that he wants a piece of the pie.

959
00:37:56,580 --> 00:37:58,090
But I do admire him.

960
00:37:58,710 --> 00:38:00,570
He's been pushed out of Qinchuan,

961
00:38:00,800 --> 00:38:02,660
yet he dares to come back for food.

962
00:38:03,110 --> 00:38:04,570
He must have some backing.

963
00:38:05,190 --> 00:38:05,590
How so?

964
00:38:05,930 --> 00:38:07,460
I saw him meeting with Xiao.

965
00:38:09,150 --> 00:38:11,410
No wonder Zhao Youlin is holding me back.

966
00:38:12,170 --> 00:38:14,370
So he went to seek out a powerful backer.

967
00:38:15,000 --> 00:38:17,000
The only question is, can his backer

968
00:38:17,280 --> 00:38:19,110
keep me in check?

969
00:38:19,800 --> 00:38:20,330
Brother,

970
00:38:22,760 --> 00:38:24,020
I plan to beat him to it.

971
00:38:28,190 --> 00:38:28,830
Forget it.

972
00:38:29,510 --> 00:38:30,720
He's come from so far away.

973
00:38:30,720 --> 00:38:33,030
We can't let him
go back empty-handed. Let him have it.

974
00:38:33,030 --> 00:38:33,560
Brother.

975
00:38:33,840 --> 00:38:34,280
Guang,

976
00:38:35,320 --> 00:38:37,380
Wen Wen is about to give birth, right?

977
00:38:39,060 --> 00:38:39,520
Soon.

978
00:38:40,230 --> 00:38:41,230
How's her health?

979
00:38:41,480 --> 00:38:42,540
Her health is good.

980
00:38:43,440 --> 00:38:45,710
It's just that
her temper is getting weirder.

981
00:38:45,710 --> 00:38:46,920
I didn't do anything.

982
00:38:47,150 --> 00:38:48,810
She just mopes around all day.

983
00:38:50,770 --> 00:38:52,730
Spend more time with her at this time.

984
00:38:52,730 --> 00:38:53,590
Don't go down the pit anymore.

985
00:38:53,590 --> 00:38:54,120
Brother,

986
00:38:54,800 --> 00:38:55,600
I was thinking

987
00:38:56,230 --> 00:38:57,630
of asking you for a favor.

988
00:38:57,920 --> 00:38:58,580
What favor?

989
00:38:58,880 --> 00:39:00,010
Name the baby for me.

990
00:39:00,190 --> 00:39:03,110
Otherwise, we won't know
what to call it when it's born.

991
00:39:03,110 --> 00:39:04,570
I'll think about it later.

992
00:39:04,630 --> 00:39:04,960
Okay.

993
00:39:28,670 --> 00:39:29,200
Who is it?

994
00:39:30,550 --> 00:39:32,230
You two are cut from the same cloth.

995
00:39:32,230 --> 00:39:33,890
How can you not recognize him?

996
00:39:35,440 --> 00:39:37,670
Your kid is quite a smart one.

997
00:39:39,590 --> 00:39:42,050
He just won
first place in the Math Olympiad.

998
00:39:42,190 --> 00:39:43,000
Impressive.

999
00:39:44,760 --> 00:39:46,690
Do you remember what grade he's in?

1000
00:39:50,030 --> 00:39:51,890
He's in middle school now, right?

1001
00:39:54,670 --> 00:39:55,600
So you know that.

1002
00:39:58,110 --> 00:39:59,150
You, as a father,

1003
00:40:00,360 --> 00:40:01,220
you're in here,

1004
00:40:01,390 --> 00:40:02,650
and you've got it easy.

1005
00:40:03,550 --> 00:40:05,480
There's a mess of trouble outside,

1006
00:40:05,710 --> 00:40:07,910
left for his mother and him to deal with.

1007
00:40:07,970 --> 00:40:10,570
Do you know how
the children of criminals live?

1008
00:40:11,700 --> 00:40:12,300
They carry

1009
00:40:12,710 --> 00:40:14,170
a mountain on their backs.

1010
00:40:15,760 --> 00:40:17,280
Some can't bear it

1011
00:40:18,320 --> 00:40:20,400
and follow in
their parents' criminal footsteps.

1012
00:40:20,400 --> 00:40:21,800
They either steal or rob.

1013
00:40:22,590 --> 00:40:23,450
Of course, some

1014
00:40:24,190 --> 00:40:25,960
are self-reliant and strong.

1015
00:40:26,920 --> 00:40:29,120
They swallow their pain and keep going.

1016
00:40:31,920 --> 00:40:33,920
Your kid belongs to the second type.

1017
00:40:34,190 --> 00:40:35,650
To be honest, I'm a father too.

1018
00:40:35,650 --> 00:40:36,280
My kid

1019
00:40:36,810 --> 00:40:38,270
doesn't compare to yours.

1020
00:40:42,910 --> 00:40:44,640
Let me tell you something else.

1021
00:40:45,840 --> 00:40:47,570
The other day, I asked your kid,

1022
00:40:48,550 --> 00:40:49,280
"Bao,

1023
00:40:49,800 --> 00:40:51,200
do you hate your father?"

1024
00:40:52,670 --> 00:40:53,730
Guess what he said?

1025
00:40:56,280 --> 00:40:57,610
He didn't say anything.

1026
00:40:59,440 --> 00:41:01,040
He nodded slightly at first,

1027
00:41:01,720 --> 00:41:03,990
then shook his head vigorously.

1028
00:41:06,230 --> 00:41:07,920
His eyes were full of tears,

1029
00:41:09,280 --> 00:41:10,400
biting his lip hard

1030
00:41:11,000 --> 00:41:12,460
to keep them from falling.

1031
00:41:15,630 --> 00:41:17,190
You have such a good kid.

1032
00:41:18,230 --> 00:41:19,290
What should you do?

1033
00:41:21,800 --> 00:41:23,130
I don't need to tell you.

1034
00:41:53,600 --> 00:41:54,130
Brother,

1035
00:41:54,510 --> 00:41:56,710
why did you bring back
the remaining half bag?

1036
00:41:56,710 --> 00:41:57,800
Chefs need to taste
their dishes, you know.

1037
00:41:57,800 --> 00:41:59,550
Just checking if the flavor is right.

1038
00:41:59,550 --> 00:42:00,250
Your skills

1039
00:42:00,550 --> 00:42:02,210
are definitely not a problem.

1040
00:42:03,200 --> 00:42:03,860
No problem.

1041
00:42:09,590 --> 00:42:10,790
It's lined up, right?

1042
00:42:13,320 --> 00:42:14,520
Which one goes where?

1043
00:42:17,630 --> 00:42:18,830
It should be correct.

1044
00:42:19,090 --> 00:42:19,750
Ready.

1045
00:42:25,800 --> 00:42:26,510
What's wrong, brother?

1046
00:42:26,510 --> 00:42:28,110
Didn't you say I was capable?

1047
00:42:28,240 --> 00:42:29,480
What's wrong? Don't you believe me?

1048
00:42:29,480 --> 00:42:32,660
It's not that. I just see you
always carrying that little notebook.

1049
00:42:32,660 --> 00:42:33,840
It must be very precise.

1050
00:42:33,840 --> 00:42:34,590
If you think it's precise,

1051
00:42:34,590 --> 00:42:35,720
why do you need this?

1052
00:42:36,850 --> 00:42:38,310
If we die, we die together.

1053
00:42:38,960 --> 00:42:40,690
I'm not afraid. I'm not afraid.

1054
00:42:43,760 --> 00:42:44,390
Get ready.
